WEBVTT

00:02:40.933 --> 00:02:43.039
Na mpenzi nimezeeka na majuto

00:02:43.063 --> 00:02:45.555
nikitamani ningekushikilia na kusahau tu.

00:02:45.579 --> 00:02:48.447
Ila siwezi nitakuwa tu nyumbani
huku nikitamani nyumbani,

00:02:48.471 --> 00:02:51.590
nikitamani ungekuwa wangu
na sikukuumiza kama nilivyofanya.

00:02:51.614 --> 00:02:53.910
Hatuwezi kurudi pale ambapo
tulikuwa na nafasi,

00:02:53.934 --> 00:02:56.205
Nikitamani ningejaribu mapenzi ya kweli.

00:02:56.229 --> 00:03:00.496
Sasa nagundua vitu vyote ningewezapata
vilikuwa kwenye mikono yako baridi.